    },
    {
      "text": "Zero4 Champ RR (ゼロヨンチャンプ ダブルアール) is a 1994 racing  video game developed and published by Media Rings for the Super Famicom. The game is about an 18-year-old race car driver who must chase his dreams of drag racing after being turned down for university and becoming a rōnin due to his joblessness status. The game received a sequel, Zero4 Champ RR-Z.",
      "lang": "en",
